    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source for parts. The engine is currently suffering from significant oil leaks and chronic overheating issues, meaning it is not currently roadworthy. The exterior has several deep dents and widespread rust, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please come prepared with a trailer, as this car will need to be towed.",
